==English==

===Etymology===
From the English slang word ''[[chick]]'', "girl", "woman", + English ''[[flick]]'', "film", "movie", probably a derivation from "to [[flicker]]".

===Noun===
'''[[chick]] [[flick]]'''  (''plural:'' '''[[chick flicks]]''')
# (''slang'') A [[film]], usually about [[relationship]]s, which is [[popular]] with [[female]]s and comparatively unpopular with males.

